    <text>     
        <body>
            
            <div type="page" xml:id="pg_15">
                
                <div type="panelGrp" xml:id="eg_0001">
                    
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="1"  characters="#grampa #child1 #child2"> <!-- Done -->
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="grampa">
                            Then there are <emph rendition="#b ">HARVESTER</emph> ants, that gather seeds and store them in barns underground.
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#child2">
                            I guess they <emph rendition="#b ">PLANT</emph> the seeds an' grow stuff, huh?
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#child1">
                            Oh, sure!
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> Grampa continues to tell the children that ants can gatehr seeds and store thhem underground. A panel thought bubble can be seen appearing from the second child, showing what they are imagining this scenario looking like. 
                        </note>
                    </cbml:panel> 
                    
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#grampa #child1 #child2"> <!-- Done -->
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#grampa"> 
                            No... but there <emph rendition="#b ">ARE</emph> ants that grow <emph rendition="#b ">MUSHROOMS</emph> to eat!
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#child1">
                            Aw, c'mon, Grampa!
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> There is a thought bubble showing ants in a field harvesting mushrooms. Grampa continues to tell the children about ants.
                        </note> 
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    
                    <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#grampa #child1 #child2"> <!-- Done -->
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#grampa">
                            Oh, yes! And have you heard of <emph rendition="#b ">CARPENTER</emph> ants, that build their nests inside trees?
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#child1">
                            They have little <emph rendition="#b ">HAMMERS</emph> an' <emph rendition="#b ">SAWS,</emph> s'pose!
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#child2">
                            Tee hee!
                        </cbml:balloon>
                        <note type="panelDesc"> Grampa tells them of "carpenter" ants and how they build their nests within trees. The children imagine these ants having tools such as hammers and saws to create their homes.
                        </note> 
                    </cbml:panel>
                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
